OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSunny start for most,
OL,6,Fperhaps cloudier in the north, before
OL,7,Fthicker cloud spreads south through
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Likely dry, but very
OL,9,Fisolated showers possible later. Very
OL,10,Fwarm again, but breezier.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCooler
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells and showers Sunday,
OL,14,Fthese perhaps heavy at times. Dry for
OL,15,Fmost Monday, with lighter winds,
OL,16,Fvariable cloud and sunny periods. Warm
OL,17,Fagain Tuesday, with sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
